'''Fel's Day''' was a holiday observed every year on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal IV]], to mark the efforts of [[Baron/Legends|Baron]] [[Soontir Fel/Legends|Soontir Fel]] in defending the planet from attack by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. This holiday was first commemorated by [[Lon Isoto]].

